ipinfo-infobox-title: Text of the header for a box that shows information from the widget
ipinfo-property-label-isp: Label for Internet Service Provider (ISP) data returned
ipinfo-property-label-asn: Label for Autonomous System Number (ASN) data returned (an ASN refers to a block of IP addresses)
ipinfo-property-label-organization: Label for Autonomous System Organization data returned
ipinfo-property-label-connectiontype: Label for the connection method data returned
ipinfo-property-label-usertype: Label for the connection owner data returned
ipinfo-property-label-source: Label for where data displayed comes from
ipinfo-property-tooltip-connectiontype: Additional information about the connection method info
ipinfo-property-tooltip-usertype: Additional information about the connection owner info
ipinfo-value-active-blocks:
Message for displaying the active blocks data. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of blocks.
ipinfo-property-label-edits:
Label for both recent and local edits

{{Identical|Contribution}}
ipinfo-value-local-edits:
Message for displaying the local edits data. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of edits.
ipinfo-value-recent-edits:
Message for displaying the recent edits data. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of edits.
ipinfo-property-no-data: Returned when no data is available for a property
ipinfo-widget-error-default: Error message shown in the widget.
ipinfo-widget-error-no-data:
Error message shown in the widget.

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of a data source
ipinfo-widget-error-wrong-ip: Error message shown in the widget.
ipinfo-widget-error-ip-no-edits: Error message shown in the infobox widget
ipinfo-preference-enable:
Used in [[Special:Preferences]].

Label for a checkbox to enable/disable the IP info feature.
ipinfo-preference-use-agreement:
Used in [[Special:Preferences]] and on [[Special:Contributions]].

Label for a checkbox to enable/disable the IP info feature
ipinfo-infobox-use-terms: Used on [[Special:Contributions]] to describe information provided by IP Info
ipinfo-infobox-submit-agreement: Used for the user agreement form on [[Special:Contributions]]
ipinfo-infobox-disable-instructions: Used for the user agreement form on [[Special:Contributions]]
ipinfo-use-agreement-submit-error: Used for the user agreement form on [[Special:Contributions]]
ipinfo-rest-access-denied: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when access is denied.
ipinfo-rest-access-denied-blocked-user: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when access is denied because the user is blocked.
ipinfo-rest-revision-no-author: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when a user does not have permission to read the author of a revision.
ipinfo-rest-revision-registered: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when a revision belongs to a registered user.
ipinfo-rest-log-nonexistent: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when a log entry does not exist.
ipinfo-rest-log-registered: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when a log entry belongs to a registered user.
ipinfo-rest-log-denied: Error message for REST API debugging, shown when a user does not have permission to read the performer of a log entry.
ipinfo-source-geoip2: Disclaimer about the accuracy of the data, MaxMind is the provider name, GeoIP2 is the collection of their databases.
prefs-ipinfo: Text of a section header in [[Special:Preferences]].
